<h1 local-id=3D"f92291fc0732" id=3D"Backenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-1.=C3=81t=
tekint=C3=A9s">1. =C3=81ttekint=C3=A9s</h1>
<p local-id=3D"2476c27b2951">A Planova backend egy .NET 8 alap=C3=BA RESTfu=
l Web API, amely a Planova napt=C3=A1r-<br>
=C3=A9s produktivit=C3=A1s-alkalmaz=C3=A1s szerveroldali logik=C3=A1j=C3=A1=
t biztos=C3=ADtja.</p>
<p local-id=3D"734bd4f9f39d">Az API JWT-alap=C3=BA hiteles=C3=ADt=C3=A9st, =
Entity Framework Core-on kereszt=C3=BCli adatb=C3=A1zis-kezel=C3=A9st,<br>
valamint <strong>*</strong>SignalR val=C3=B3s idej=C5=B1 kommunik=C3=A1ci=
=C3=B3t haszn=C3=A1l.</p>
<p local-id=3D"611955e16fb1"><strong>Keretrendszer</strong>: .NET 8 (C#)<br=
><strong>Adatb=C3=A1zis</strong>: PostgreSQL (Npgsql provider)<br><strong>O=
RM</strong>: Entity Framework Core 8<br><strong>Hiteles=C3=ADt=C3=A9s</stro=
ng>: JWT Bearer (access + refresh token)<br><strong>*Val=C3=B3s idej=C5=B1<=
/strong>: Entity Framework Core SignalR<br><strong>API dokument=C3=A1ci=C3=
=B3</strong>: Swagger / OpenAPI (Swashbuckle)<br><strong>Projektkezel=C3=A9=
s</strong>: User Secrets a szenzit=C3=ADv konfigur=C3=A1ci=C3=B3hoz</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"70b558aa2f0e" id=3D"Backenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-2.Projekt=
strukt=C3=BAra">2. Projektstrukt=C3=BAra</h1>
<p local-id=3D"51338b318784"><strong>apps/backend/backendAPI/</strong><br>
 Program.cs =E2=80=93 Alkalmaz=C3=A1s bel=C3=A9p=C3=A9si pont =C3=A9s szolg=
=C3=A1ltat=C3=A1s-konfigur=C3=A1ci=C3=B3<br>
 appsettings.json =E2=80=93 Alkalmaz=C3=A1s be=C3=A1ll=C3=ADt=C3=A1sok =C3=
=A9s connection string<br>
 Controllers/ =E2=80=93 API kontrollerek (9 db)<br>
 Models/ =E2=80=93 Entit=C3=A1s modellek (9 db)<br>
 Models/Enums/ =E2=80=93 Felsorol=C3=A1s t=C3=ADpusok (5 db)<br>
 DTOs/ =E2=80=93 Adat=C3=A1tviteli objektumok (modulonk=C3=A9nt csoportos=
=C3=ADtva)<br>
 Services/ =E2=80=93 =C3=9Czleti logika =C3=A9s valid=C3=A1l=C3=A1s (10 szo=
lg=C3=A1ltat=C3=A1s)<br>
 Data/ =E2=80=93 DbContext =C3=A9s modell konfigur=C3=A1ci=C3=B3k<br>
 Data/ModelConfigurations/ =E2=80=93 Fluent API entit=C3=A1s konfigur=C3=A1=
ci=C3=B3k (9 db)<br>
 Hubs/ =E2=80=93 SignalR hub =C3=A9s felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3-azonos=C3=ADt=C3=
=B3 provider<br>
 Common/ =E2=80=93 K=C3=B6z=C3=B6s hibakonstansok<br>
 Extensions/ =E2=80=93 Controller extension met=C3=B3dusok<br>
 Migrations/ =E2=80=93 EF Core migr=C3=A1ci=C3=B3k (5 db)</p>
<p local-id=3D"4332b314f039"><strong>apps/backend/backendTests/</strong> =
=E2=80=93 Egys=C3=A9gtesztek (xUnit)</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"385e53a3b73c" id=3D"Backenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-3.Konfigu=
r=C3=A1ci=C3=B3=C3=A9sind=C3=ADt=C3=A1s">3. Konfigur=C3=A1ci=C3=B3 =C3=A9s =
ind=C3=ADt=C3=A1s</h1>
<p local-id=3D"9d6e71dfd925"><strong>3.1. Adatb=C3=A1zis kapcsolat</strong>=
</p>
<p local-id=3D"cdbac3a8a7a5">A connection string az appsettings.json f=C3=
=A1jlban tal=C3=A1lhat=C3=B3, a felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3n=C3=A9v<br>
 =C3=A9s jelsz=C3=B3 hely=C5=91rz=C5=91ket ({USERNAME}, {PASSWORD}) User Se=
crets-b=C5=91l t=C3=B6lti be:</p>
<p local-id=3D"3047047cd72d">Host=3Dlocalhost;Port=3D5432;Database=3DVizsga=
remek;<br>
 Username=3D{USERNAME};Password=3D{PASSWORD};Trust Server Certificate=3Dtru=
e</p>
<p local-id=3D"bae6aef2d1a8"><strong>3.2. JWT konfigur=C3=A1ci=C3=B3</stron=
g></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3530e4f08fb2">
<li local-id=3D"b3511a88e440">
<p local-id=3D"e6ff65893705">Issuer =C3=A9s Audience: appsettings.json-ban =
(AppSettings szekci=C3=B3)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0a5ff2b9543f">
<p local-id=3D"09dac803e8a5">Titkos kulcs: User Secrets-ben (jwt-secret-key=
)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"03e53a760027">
<p local-id=3D"35b26b93ff8c">Token =C3=A9rv=C3=A9nyess=C3=A9g: r=C3=B6vid =
=C3=A9lettartam=C3=BA access token + 7 napos refresh token</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8fdbe6694744">
<p local-id=3D"72126adba62d">Claims: UserId (NameIdentifier), Email, Profil=
eId, IssuedAt, JwtId</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f3127e626280"><strong>3.3. Szolg=C3=A1ltat=C3=A1s-regisztr=
=C3=A1ci=C3=B3</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"5189b627804c">Minden =C3=BCzleti szolg=C3=A1ltat=C3=A1s Scop=
ed =C3=A9letciklussal regisztr=C3=A1l=C3=B3dik a DI kont=C3=A9nerbe.<br>
 A SignalR felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3-provider Singleton-k=C3=A9nt regisztr=C3=
=A1l=C3=B3dik.</p>
<p local-id=3D"4337df9a4200"><strong>3.4. Middleware pipeline</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"747458227469">HTTPS =C3=A1tir=C3=A1ny=C3=ADt=C3=A1s =E2=86=
=92 CORS =E2=86=92 Authentication =E2=86=92 Authorization =E2=86=92 SignalR=
 hub<br>
 mapping =E2=86=92 Controller mapping</p>
<p local-id=3D"d15a48c1c882"><strong>3.5. CORS</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"bbeae2b33306">Enged=C3=A9lyezett origin: <a class=3D"externa=
l-link" href=3D"http://localhost:3000" rel=3D"nofollow">http://localhost:30=
00</a><br>
 Enged=C3=A9lyezett: minden header, minden met=C3=B3dus, hiteles=C3=ADt=C5=
=91 adatok (credentials)</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"fa85e59e2757" id=3D"Backenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-4.Adatmod=
ell(entit=C3=A1sok)">4. Adatmodell (entit=C3=A1sok)</h1>
<p local-id=3D"25115ac82391"><strong>4.1. User</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"dc7b72e6a959">Mez=C5=91k:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"44ed72fb8100">
<li local-id=3D"a40363fef4c8">
<p local-id=3D"e26a74ca7ee8">Id (Guid, PK) =E2=80=93 Egyedi azonos=C3=ADt=
=C3=B3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"04cc3cf00110">
<p local-id=3D"4500312bbfdb">Email (string, unique, required) =E2=80=93 E-m=
ail c=C3=ADm</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d4d0d2f41b4d">
<p local-id=3D"d133c53a1d82">PasswordHash (string, required) =E2=80=93 Hash=
-elt jelsz=C3=B3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b6137a2ed9b">
<p local-id=3D"0ba310a3cd43">RefreshToken (string, nullable) =E2=80=93 Aktu=
=C3=A1lis refresh token</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b9d618aa367a">
<p local-id=3D"ae3f2ecbc5cc">RefreshTokenExpiryTime (DateTime?)=E2=80=93 Re=
fresh token lej=C3=A1rati ideje</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b12c886c053">
<p local-id=3D"d368ff398122">CreatedAt (DateTime) =E2=80=93 L=C3=A9trehoz=
=C3=A1s d=C3=A1tuma (UTC)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"76596e2d9687">Kapcsolat: egy User-hez egy Profile tartozik</=
p>
<p local-id=3D"fe39f26f0c2b"><strong>4.2. Profile</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"b75ec35f96b9">Mez=C5=91k:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"eea994fb752f">
<li local-id=3D"913d6d7b26d4">
<p local-id=3D"b5b2a6dff48f">Id (Guid, PK) =E2=80=93 Egyedi azonos=C3=ADt=
=C3=B3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21ff98d3ae58">
<p local-id=3D"aa4d12ec6ce9">Username (string, 3-64 kar., unique) =E2=80=93=
 Felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3n=C3=A9v</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9ab08109389a">
<p local-id=3D"b68e934e6bb5">Avatar (string, required) =E2=80=93 Avatar azo=
nos=C3=ADt=C3=B3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"273a86cf45ab">
<p local-id=3D"3a5ea8f5dcc5">IsPrivate (bool) =E2=80=93 Priv=C3=A1t profil =
jelz=C5=91</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"348ace545def">
<p local-id=3D"226c79734f9d">FirstName (string, max 128, nullable)=E2=80=93=
 Keresztn=C3=A9v</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"889925ae8071">
<p local-id=3D"6349d910ee91">LastName (string, max 128, nullable) =E2=80=93=
 Vezet=C3=A9kn=C3=A9v</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a31d0876ac6a">
<p local-id=3D"51c32ad8bbae">BirthDate (DateOnly, nullable) =E2=80=93 Sz=C3=
=BClet=C3=A9si d=C3=A1tum</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"091a9db62987">
