<h1 local-id=3D"74b4686bd764" id=3D"Backenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-6.APIv=C3=
=A9gpontok(kontrollerek)">6. API v=C3=A9gpontok (kontrollerek)</h1>
<p local-id=3D"8b5f2b39b81f">Minden kontroller az api/ =C3=BAtvonal-prefix =
alatt =C3=A9rhet=C5=91 el.<br>
Az <strong>[Authorize]</strong> jel=C3=B6l=C3=A9ssel ell=C3=A1tott v=C3=A9g=
pontok JWT hiteles=C3=ADt=C3=A9st ig=C3=A9nyelnek.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8a314a5dc6cd"><strong>6.1. AuthController (api/Auth)</strong=
></p>
<p local-id=3D"341880f7bfdf"><strong> POST api/Auth/sign-up</strong><br>
 Le=C3=ADr=C3=A1s: =C3=9Aj felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3 regisztr=C3=A1l=C3=A1sa<br=
>
 Body: SignUpRequestDTO { Email, Password }<br>
 V=C3=A1lasz: 200 OK / 400 BadRequest (hiba=C3=BCzenet)<br>
 Logika: Tranzakci=C3=B3ban l=C3=A9trehozza a User-t, Profile-t =C3=A9s egy=
<br>
 alap=C3=A9rtelmezett Calendar-t. A felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3n=C3=A9v az e-mail=
<br>
 @ el=C5=91tti r=C3=A9sz=C3=A9b=C5=91l gener=C3=A1l=C3=B3dik (egyedis=C3=A9=
g biztos=C3=ADtott).</p>
<p local-id=3D"6016dd4a17f6"><strong> POST api/Auth/sign-in</strong><br>
 Le=C3=ADr=C3=A1s: Bejelentkez=C3=A9s<br>
 Body: SignInRequestDTO { Email, Password }<br>
 V=C3=A1lasz: 200 OK + TokenResponseDTO / 400 BadRequest<br>
 Logika: Jelsz=C3=B3 ellen=C5=91rz=C3=A9s PasswordHasher-rel. Sikeres bejel=
entkez=C3=A9s<br>
 eset=C3=A9n JWT access token =C3=A9s refresh token gener=C3=A1l=C3=A1sa.<b=
r>
 A tokenek HttpOnly cookie-kban is be=C3=A1ll=C3=ADt=C3=B3dnak (web kliens<=
br>
 sz=C3=A1m=C3=A1ra) =C3=A9s a v=C3=A1lasz body-ban is visszat=C3=A9rnek (mo=
bil kliens<br>
 sz=C3=A1m=C3=A1ra).</p>
<p local-id=3D"5292332fe5a9"><strong> GET api/Auth/refresh</strong><br>
 Le=C3=ADr=C3=A1s: Token friss=C3=ADt=C3=A9s<br>
 Forr=C3=A1s: Cookie-kb=C3=B3l VAGY Authorization + X-Refresh-Token header-=
b=C5=91l<br>
 V=C3=A1lasz: 200 OK + TokenResponseDTO / 401 Unauthorized<br>
 Logika: A lej=C3=A1rt access tokenb=C5=91l kinyeri a UserId-t (ValidateLif=
etime<br>
 =3D false), ellen=C5=91rzi a refresh token =C3=A9rv=C3=A9nyess=C3=A9g=C3=
=A9t, majd =C3=BAj<br>
 token-p=C3=A1rt gener=C3=A1l.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5b60f7d7d46a"><strong> GET api/Auth/sign-out</strong><br>
 Le=C3=ADr=C3=A1s: Kijelentkez=C3=A9s<br>
 V=C3=A1lasz: 200 OK<br>
 Logika: T=C3=B6rli az accessToken =C3=A9s refreshToken cookie-kat.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8a9e1c8ed4ae"><strong> GET api/Auth/verify [Authorize]</stro=
ng><br>
 Le=C3=ADr=C3=A1s: JWT =C3=A9rv=C3=A9nyess=C3=A9g ellen=C5=91rz=C3=A9se<br>
 V=C3=A1lasz: 200 OK / 401 Unauthorized</p>
<p local-id=3D"dc0838d676d3"><strong>6.2. CalendarController (api/Calendar)=
</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"55c40333a992"><strong> GET api/Calendar [Authorize]</strong>=
<br>
 Le=C3=ADr=C3=A1s: Felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3 =C3=B6sszes napt=C3=A1r=C3=A1nak l=
ek=C3=A9r=C3=A9se<br>
 V=C3=A1lasz: 200 OK + GetCalendarDTO[]<br>
 Logika: UNION lek=C3=A9rdez=C3=A9ssel =C3=B6sszevonja a saj=C3=A1t napt=C3=
=A1rakat =C3=A9s a<br>
 megosztott napt=C3=A1rakat.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5750ab970c93"><strong> POST api/Calendar [Authorize]</strong=
><br>
 Le=C3=ADr=C3=A1s: =C3=9Aj napt=C3=A1r l=C3=A9trehoz=C3=A1sa<br>
 Body: CreateCalendarDTO { Name, Color }<br>
 V=C3=A1lasz: 200 OK / 400 BadRequest<br>
 Logika: Napt=C3=A1rn=C3=A9v valid=C3=A1l=C3=A1s (3-32 karakter), majd ment=
=C3=A9s.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a5b4a7c7f582"><strong> PUT api/Calendar/{calendarId} [Author=
ize]</strong><br>
 Le=C3=ADr=C3=A1s: Napt=C3=A1r m=C3=B3dos=C3=ADt=C3=A1sa<br>
 Body: UpdateCalendarDTO { Id, Name, Color }<br>
 V=C3=A1lasz: 200 OK / 400 BadRequest<br>
 Logika: Jogosults=C3=A1g-ellen=C5=91rz=C3=A9s (tulajdonos vagy Editor szer=
epk=C3=B6r=C5=B1<br>
 megosztott felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3), valid=C3=A1l=C3=A1s, majd friss=C3=ADt=
=C3=A9s.</p>
<p local-id=3D"da5e0e3f4042"><strong> DELETE api/Calendar/{calendarId} [Aut=
horize]</strong><br>
 Le=C3=ADr=C3=A1s: Napt=C3=A1r t=C3=B6rl=C3=A9se<br>
 V=C3=A1lasz: 204 NoContent / 400 BadRequest<br>
 Logika: Kaszk=C3=A1d t=C3=B6rl=C3=A9s: el=C5=91sz=C3=B6r a napt=C3=A1rbeje=
gyz=C3=A9sek, majd a<br>
 megoszt=C3=A1sok, v=C3=A9g=C3=BCl maga a napt=C3=A1r.</p>
<p local-id=3D"01086474449c"><strong>6.3. CalendarEntryController (api/Cale=
ndarEntry)</strong></p>
