<h1 local-id=3D"3d10142f42a7" id=3D"Backenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-7.Adat=C3=
=A1tviteliobjektumok(DTO-k)">7. Adat=C3=A1tviteli objektumok (DTO-k)</h1>
<p local-id=3D"b6353b49245b"><strong>7.1. Auth DTOs</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"f9db78f7a15e">SignUpRequestDTO<br>
 - Email (string)<br>
 - Password (string)</p>
<p local-id=3D"7e0ad6a3d2eb">SignInRequestDTO<br>
 - Email (string)<br>
 - Password (string)</p>
<p local-id=3D"568b3f76a2d7">TokenResponseDTO<br>
 - AccessToken (string, required)<br>
 - RefreshToken (string, required)</p>
<p local-id=3D"e8aa739b875a"><strong>7.2. Calendar DTOs</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"6c9045b219e2">CreateCalendarDTO<br>
 - Name (string, required)<br>
 - Color (int)</p>
<p local-id=3D"47e7ff92be8b">GetCalendarDTO<br>
 - Id (Guid)<br>
 - Name (string)<br>
 - Color (int)</p>
<p local-id=3D"9690662bd509">UpdateCalendarDTO<br>
 - Id (Guid)<br>
 - Name (string, required)<br>
 - Color (int)</p>
<p local-id=3D"143d6923f420">AccessibleCalendarDTO<br>
 - CalendarId (Guid)<br>
 - Role (Role enum)</p>
<p local-id=3D"0b0e6dfd16b1"><strong>7.3. CalendarEntry DTOs</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"ca658c5f361f">CreateCalendarEntryDTO<br>
 - EntryCategory (EntryCategory enum)<br>
 - Name (string, required)<br>
 - Description (string, nullable)<br>
 - StartDate (DateTime)<br>
 - EndDate (DateTime)<br>
 - Location (string, nullable)<br>
 - NotificationTime (DateTime, nullable)<br>
 - Color (int, nullable)<br>
 - IsAllDay (bool, nullable)<br>
 - CalendarId (Guid)</p>
<p local-id=3D"eebff8955148">GetCalendarEntryDTO<br>
 - A fenti mez=C5=91k + Id, IsCompleted, CalendarName, CreatedBy,<br>
 CreatedByName</p>
<p local-id=3D"0308efc76850">UpdateCalendarEntryDTO<br>
 - A CreateCalendarEntryDTO mez=C5=91i + Id, IsCompleted</p>
<p local-id=3D"c1116450cc76">GetCalendarEntriesRequestDTO<br>
 - StartDate (DateTime, nullable)<br>
 - EndDate (DateTime, nullable)<br>
 - Ids (List&lt;string&gt;)</p>
<p local-id=3D"a9052b0bd38f"><strong>*7.4. Friend DTOs</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"e48a21df702d">AddFriendDTO<br>
 - ProfileId (Guid)</p>
