 - Status (Status enum)<br>
 - CreatedAt (DateTime)<br>
 - UpdatedAt (DateTime, nullable)</p>
<p local-id=3D"61e00e1ec6cf">UpdateFriendStatus<br>
 - ProfileId (Guid)<br>
 - Status (Status enum)</p>
<p local-id=3D"e4a77b5cb990"><strong>*7.5. Habit DTOs</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"18a1d5cf1a02">CreateHabitDto<br>
 - Name (string, required)<br>
 - Description (string, nullable)<br>
 - Habitcategory (HabitCategory enum)<br>
 - Unit (Unit enum)<br>
 - Goal (float, nullable)<br>
 - Days (int, nullable)<br>
 - Color (int)</p>
<p local-id=3D"a962e1ef9a02">GetHabitsDto<br>
 - A fenti mez=C5=91k + ProfileUsername, HabitCategory</p>
<p local-id=3D"5a206182192d">UpdateHabitDto<br>
 - A fenti mez=C5=91k + Id</p>
<p local-id=3D"a084f515e2a8"><strong>*7.6. Profile DTOs</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"38779077ea85">CreateProfileDTO<br>
 - Username (string, required)<br>
