 - UserEmail (string)</p>
<p local-id=3D"9044acafe40c">UpdateProfileDTO<br>
 - Id (Guid)<br>
 - Username, Avatar (string, required)<br>
 - IsPrivate (bool)<br>
 - FirstName, LastName, BirthDate<br>
