<p local-id=3D"6aade40bf906"><strong>7.8. Generikus v=C3=A1lasz</strong></p=
>
<p local-id=3D"ae6aee50f400">ServiceResponse&lt;T&gt;<br>
 - Data (T, nullable) =E2=80=93 Visszat=C3=A9r=C3=A9si adat<br>
 - Success (bool) =E2=80=93 Sikeres-e a m=C5=B1velet<br>
 - Message (string?) =E2=80=93 Hiba=C3=BCzenet sikertelen esetben</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"5e98c3a98416" id=3D"Backenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-8.Szolg=
=C3=A1ltat=C3=A1sr=C3=A9teg(services)">8. Szolg=C3=A1ltat=C3=A1s r=C3=A9teg=
 (services)</h1>
<p local-id=3D"4cfb3ffade52">Minden szolg=C3=A1ltat=C3=A1s interf=C3=A9sz +=
 implement=C3=A1ci=C3=B3 p=C3=A1rosk=C3=A9nt van megval=C3=B3s=C3=ADtva,<br=
>
=C3=A9s Scoped =C3=A9letciklussal regisztr=C3=A1l=C3=B3dik a DI kont=C3=A9n=
erbe.</p>
<p local-id=3D"936d692c640e"><strong>8.1. AuthService (IAuthService)</stron=
g></p>
<p local-id=3D"e929039ffb46">Felel=C5=91ss=C3=A9g: Felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3 hi=
teles=C3=ADt=C3=A9se =C3=A9s token-kezel=C3=A9s</p>
<p local-id=3D"04f6d4ed7746">Met=C3=B3dusok:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dca14642fc7a">
<li local-id=3D"213d8e9ec56e">
<p local-id=3D"76f40f950390">SignUpAsync(SignUpRequestDTO) =E2=86=92 Servic=
eResponse&lt;Guid&gt;<br>
E-mail form=C3=A1tum =C3=A9s jelsz=C3=B3 er=C5=91ss=C3=A9g valid=C3=A1l=C3=
=A1s, duplik=C3=A1lt e-mail<br>
ellen=C5=91rz=C3=A9s, jelsz=C3=B3 hash-el=C3=A9s (PasswordHasher&lt;User&gt=
;), ment=C3=A9s.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d91af6ff896">
<p local-id=3D"82d9e488409f">SignInAsync(SignInRequestDTO) =E2=86=92 TokenR=
esponseDTO?<br>
Felhaszn=C3=A1l=C3=B3 keres=C3=A9se e-mail alapj=C3=A1n, jelsz=C3=B3 verifi=
k=C3=A1ci=C3=B3,<br>
JWT access token =C3=A9s refresh token gener=C3=A1l=C3=A1s.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f8fbc0e01dd">
<p local-id=3D"5ef72fb7da5d">RefreshTokensAsync(TokenResponseDTO) =E2=86=92=
 TokenResponseDTO?<br>
Lej=C3=A1rt access tokenb=C5=91l UserId kinyer=C3=A9se, refresh token valid=
=C3=A1l=C3=A1s<br>
az adatb=C3=A1zisb=C3=B3l, =C3=BAj token-p=C3=A1r gener=C3=A1l=C3=A1s.</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"eb5de1ef8165">Bels=C5=91 seg=C3=A9dmethods:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9c1001b49de0">
<li local-id=3D"4576388860d9">
<p local-id=3D"03c1178db4f6">CreateToken() =E2=80=93 JWT token gener=C3=A1l=
=C3=A1s (claims: UserId, Email,<br>
ProfileId, IssuedAt, JwtId)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"315ec70015fd">
<p local-id=3D"428d48bb5e96">GenerateRefreshToken() =E2=80=93 32 b=C3=A1jto=
s kriptogr=C3=A1fiai random token</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"036c2617ba47">
<p local-id=3D"ac210c922dde">GenerateAndSaveRefreshTokenAsync() =E2=80=93 R=
efresh token ment=C3=A9s DB-be<br>
(7 napos lej=C3=A1rat)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"64d739da9392">
<p local-id=3D"edc1384422f7">GetUserIdFromExpiredToken() =E2=80=93 UserId k=
inyer=C3=A9se lej=C3=A1rt tokenb=C5=91l</p></li>
