<h1 local-id=3D"360f890f45d6" id=3D"Backenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-9.Hiteles=
=C3=ADt=C3=A9s=C3=A9sjogosults=C3=A1gkezel=C3=A9s">9. Hiteles=C3=ADt=C3=A9s=
 =C3=A9s jogosults=C3=A1gkezel=C3=A9s</h1>
<p local-id=3D"c43e25a9a3d7"><strong>9.1. Token kezel=C3=A9s</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"a0f35228ac71">Access token (JWT):</p>
<ul local-id=3D"298cf6e706a8">
<li local-id=3D"cecc7549c0c4">
<p local-id=3D"950b466fffef">Claims: UserId, Email, ProfileId, IssuedAt, Jw=
tId</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"545d30d6613f">
<p local-id=3D"788c2723bdd4">Al=C3=A1=C3=ADr=C3=A1s: SymmetricSecurityKey (=
HMAC)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cdd845a1c640">
<p local-id=3D"0cff8149cebe">Valid=C3=A1l=C3=A1s: Issuer, Audience, Lifetim=
e, IssuerSigningKey</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a9664111f044">
<p local-id=3D"85c173e83f9e">ClockSkew: Zero (pontos lej=C3=A1rat)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"db15f9a3faa3">Refresh token:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"468a1b89b3c6">
<li local-id=3D"4d79b275cd75">
<p local-id=3D"b93f7339d710">32 b=C3=A1jtos RandomNumberGenerator =E2=86=92=
 Base64 string</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5b321613f604">
<p local-id=3D"b17d202f9f74">Az adatb=C3=A1zisban (User t=C3=A1bla) t=C3=A1=
rol=C3=B3dik</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"678000ffacd9">
<p local-id=3D"98be7eee7ec2">7 napos lej=C3=A1rat</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f59a23557ea5">
<p local-id=3D"32b1606a0804">Rot=C3=A1ci=C3=B3: minden friss=C3=ADt=C3=A9sk=
or =C3=BAj refresh token gener=C3=A1l=C3=B3dik</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d3ac8f0b7151"><strong>9.2. Token megszerz=C3=A9s sorrendje</=
strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"404907874bdc">A backend az al=C3=A1bbi sorrendben keresi a t=
okent:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"d88715f3a855">
<li local-id=3D"15a67d57fd1f">
<p local-id=3D"f7c5b98a3399">accessToken cookie (webes kliens)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d1b56179998d">
<p local-id=3D"fa6458f295d3">SignalR query string access_token (/notificati=
ons =C3=BAtvonalra)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"88b3594d8a03">
<p local-id=3D"59f2e871eb96">Authorization: Bearer header (Swagger/nat=C3=
=ADv kliens)</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"8ee748875f57"><strong>9.3. Jogosults=C3=A1gi szintek napt=C3=
=A1rakn=C3=A1l</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"baf3a97a4746">
<li local-id=3D"72e9396470d0">
<p local-id=3D"2896f77ec5a8">Tulajdonos: minden m=C5=B1velet enged=C3=A9lye=
zett</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"951dcff5d942">
<p local-id=3D"256a53ac73b8">Editor (megosztott): olvas=C3=A1s + szerkeszt=
=C3=A9s enged=C3=A9lyezett</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b8c35f92bf67">
<p local-id=3D"ccce7cbae56f">Viewer (megosztott): csak olvas=C3=A1s enged=
=C3=A9lyezett</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f0f1f9b02506"><strong>9.4. Controller extension met=C3=B3dus=
ok</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"64acbbcc6271">
<li local-id=3D"a9e1bfc906e8">
<p local-id=3D"9e187a46022c">GetUserId() =E2=80=93 UserId kinyer=C3=A9se a =
ClaimTypes.NameIdentifier claim-b=C5=91l</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a634a167aaa1">
<p local-id=3D"c2001f1d8889">GetProfileId() =E2=80=93 ProfileId kinyer=C3=
=A9se az egyedi "ProfileId" claim-b=C5=91l</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"1761ec6353ee" id=3D"Backenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-*10.Val=
=C3=B3sidej=C5=B1kommunik=C3=A1ci=C3=B3(SignalR)">*10. Val=C3=B3s idej=C5=
=B1 kommunik=C3=A1ci=C3=B3 (SignalR)</h1>
<p local-id=3D"b47bd1119ce0"><strong>10.1. NotificationHub</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"24fd7b8ae5b7">=C3=9Atvonal: /notifications<br>
 A hub oszt=C3=A1ly =C3=BCres, a funkcionalit=C3=A1st az IHubContext&lt;Not=
ificationHub&gt;<br>
 biztos=C3=ADtja a kontrollerekben (server-to-client push).</p>
<p local-id=3D"b13b5fff5e7d"><strong>10.2. CustomUserProvider</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"7057eb60b35b">Az IUserIdProvider implement=C3=A1ci=C3=B3ja, =
amely a SignalR kapcsolatokat<br>
 a JWT token =E2=80=9EProfileId" claim-je alapj=C3=A1n azonos=C3=ADtja. Ez =
teszi lehet=C5=91v=C3=A9,<br>
 hogy a Clients.User(profileId) h=C3=ADv=C3=A1s a megfelel=C5=91 felhaszn=
=C3=A1l=C3=B3nak<br>
 k=C3=BCldje az =C3=BCzenetet.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6b923ddd325e"><strong>10.3. Jelenleg implement=C3=A1lt =C3=
=A9rtes=C3=ADt=C3=A9sek</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"d3e794483b22">Bar=C3=A1tk=C3=A9r=C3=A9s =C3=A9rtes=C3=ADt=C3=
=A9s (FriendsController):<br>
 Esem=C3=A9ny neve: "ReceiveNotification"<br>
 Payload: { Type, Name, Message, SentAt }</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"1c8b95f5fb70" id=3D"Backenddokument=C3=A1ci=C3=B3-11.Adatb=
=C3=A1ziskonfigur=C3=A1ci=C3=B3">11. Adatb=C3=A1zis konfigur=C3=A1ci=C3=B3<=
/h1>
<p local-id=3D"35af2758fadb"><strong>11.1. AppDbContext</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"a273f355c533">DbSet-ek: Users, Profiles, Calendars, SharedCa=
lendars,<br>
 CalendarEntries, Habits, HabitLogs, Friends, EventContributors</p>
<p local-id=3D"010b57cbcb45">A modell konfigur=C3=A1ci=C3=B3k Fluent API-va=
l =C3=A9s annot=C3=A1ci=C3=B3kkal vannak defini=C3=A1lva, az<br>
 Assembly.GetExecutingAssembly()-b=C3=B3l automatikusan bet=C3=B6lt=C5=91dn=
ek<br>
 (ApplyConfigurationsFromAssembly).</p>
<p local-id=3D"4ed4452928a1"><strong>11.2. Modell konfigur=C3=A1ci=C3=B3k (=
IEntityTypeConfiguration)</strong></p>
